    "body": "<ul>\n<li><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Yes. Monitoring related alert notifications can be integrated with external services such as chats and more.</span></li>\n<li>\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Supported services are as follows.</span>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"2\"><a href=\"https://mackerel.io/docs/entry/howto/alerts/slack\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Slack</a></li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"2\">\n<a href=\"https://mackerel.io/docs/entry/howto/alerts/line\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">LINE</a><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">（※LINE WORKS is not currently supported）</span>\n</li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"2\"><a href=\"https://mackerel.io/docs/entry/howto/alerts/chatwork\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Chatwork</a></li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"2\"><a href=\"https://mackerel.io/docs/entry/howto/alerts/typetalk\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Typetalk</a></li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"2\"><a href=\"https://mackerel.io/docs/entry/howto/alerts/hipchat\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">HipChat</a></li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"2\"><a href=\"https://mackerel.io/docs/entry/howto/alerts/twilio\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Twilio</a></li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"2\"><a href=\"https://mackerel.io/docs/entry/howto/alerts/reactio\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Reactio</a></li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"2\"><a href=\"https://mackerel.io/docs/entry/howto/alerts/pagerduty\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">PagerDuty</a></li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"2\"><a href=\"https://mackerel.io/docs/entry/howto/alerts/OpsGenie\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Opsgenie</a></li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"2\"><a href=\"https://mackerel.io/docs/entry/howto/alerts/yammer\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Yammer</a></li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"2\"><a href=\"https://mackerel.io/docs/entry/howto/alerts/microsoft-teams\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Microsoft Teams</a></li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"2\"><a href=\"https://mackerel.io/docs/entry/howto/alerts/webhook\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Webhook</a></li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"2\"><a href=\"https://mackerel.io/docs/entry/howto/alerts/eventbridge\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Amazon EventBridge</a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"2\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Any service not listed above is currently not supported for integration.</span></li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"2\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">To integrate an unsupported service, you’ll need to provide your own integration mechanism using a service such as Webhook.</span></li>\n</ul>"
